plist_data.NSCameraUsageDescription: Amare uses your camera to capture progress photos that visualize your fitness transformation, scan food barcodes for quick nutrition logging, and analyze your workout form. Seeing your body change over time is incredibly motivating for women on their fitness journeys.
plist_data.NSMicrophoneUsageDescription: Amare uses your microphone for voice commands during workouts, audio notes to track your fitness journey, and hands-free operation when exercising. Voice control makes logging activities and recording observations about your wellness progress easier, especially during active workouts.
plist_data.NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription: Amare needs access to your photo library to save before/after progress photos, import food images for nutrition tracking, and create a visual record of your fitness transformation. Tracking physical changes over time provides powerful motivation and helps you celebrate your achievements.
plist_data.NSUserTrackingUsageDescription: Amare respects your privacy. We collect fitness data (workout, diet, weight) to show your progress visually and improve the app. This helps us understand your fitness patterns to optimize the interface, enhance notifications, and develop features specifically for women's fitness needs. Your data remains secure and will never be shared without your explicit consent.
plist_data.NoResponseDescription: If Amare is temporarily unresponsive, please wait a moment. Our AI fitness coach may be analyzing your workout data to provide personalized recommendations. We're dedicated to delivering thoughtful, accurate guidance tailored to women's unique fitness needs.
